Class ProjectBuildFileParserOptions.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.json.ProjectBuildFileParserOptions.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    ProjectBuildFileParserOptions

    @NotThreadSafe
public static final class ProjectBuildFileParserOptions.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    Builds instances of ProjectBuildFileParserOptions. Initialize attributes and then invoke build() method to create immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread safe and generally should not be stored in field or collection, but used immediately to create instances.
